.TH "nvme_init_identify_ns_descs_list" 9 "nvme_init_identify_ns_descs_list" "April 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_init_identify_ns_descs_list \- Initialize passthru command for Namespace Descriptor list
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" nvme_init_identify_ns_descs_list
.BI "(struct libnvme_passthru_cmd *cmd "  ","
.BI "__u32 nsid "  ","
.BI "struct nvme_ns_id_desc *descs "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "cmd" 12
Command data structure to initialize
.IP "nsid" 12
The namespace id to retrieve descriptors
.IP "descs" 12
User space destination address to transfer the data
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Initializes the passthru command buffer for the Identify command with
CNS value NVME_IDENTIFY_CNS_NS_DESC_LIST.
